                <title type="html"><![CDATA[The Lean UX Manifesto: Principle-Driven Design]]></title>
        <link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="http://www.smashingmagazine.com/2014/01/08/the-lean-ux-manifesto-principle-driven-design/"/>
        <id>http://mgmt.smashingmagazine.com/?p=179416</id>
        <updated>2014-01-08T11:28:55Z</updated>
        <published>2014-01-08T10:24:45Z</published>
            <category scheme="http://www.smashingmagazine.com" term="UX Design"/>            
        <content type="html" xml:base="http://www.smashingmagazine.com/2014/01/08/the-lean-ux-manifesto-principle-driven-design/"><![CDATA[<table width="650">
<tr>
<td width="650">
